conbody.p:
The contracting officer must submit the proposed Congressional notification through the SCO to cognizant HCA workflow at least five workdays before the proposed termination date. The cognizant HCA action officer will forward the information to SAF/LLW. The contracting officer must not release the termination notice until Congress has been notified (see 
               MP5349.7001 Congressional Notification on Significant Contract Terminations
            ).
